---
// Process from brochure page 8
---

<section class="how-we-work section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>How We Help You Buy</h2>
      <p>Simple, transparent process from start to finish</p>
    </div>

    <div class="process-steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Free Consultation</h3>
        <p>We learn about your needs, budget, and timeline through a detailed property brief</p>
        <p class="step-note">No obligation, no pressure</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline>
            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line>
            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line>
            <polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Define Your Criteria</h3>
        <p>Budget, location, property type, and must-haves</p>
        <p class="step-note">We create your customized property brief</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle>
            <path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Diligent Research & Sourcing</h3>
        <p>We search on-market AND off-market properties across Queensland</p>
        <p class="step-note">Access to exclusive deals you won't find online - we review 40+ properties weekly</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"></path>
            <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Inspections & Due Diligence</h3>
        <p>We meticulously shortlist properties and attend inspections on your behalf</p>
        <p class="step-note">Complete due diligence: building & pest inspections, flood reports, council regulations</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">5</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Strategic Negotiation</h3>
        <p>We negotiate on your behalf using our deep agent relationships</p>
        <p class="step-note">Real estate agents give our clients preference because they know deals won't fall through</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">6</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="m3 9 9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Settlement Support</h3>
        <p>We provide unwavering support through settlement proceedings</p>
        <p class="step-note">Final inspection, seamless handover, and you move into your dream property</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Fee Transparency -->
    <div class="fee-transparency">
      <div class="fee-content">
        <h3>Our Service Fees</h3>
        <p class="fee-intro">Transparent flat fee structure with no hidden costs.</p>

        <div class="fee-details">
          <div class="fee-item">
            <h4>Queensland (Brisbane & Gold Coast)</h4>
            <p class="fee-amount">Typically 2-3% of purchase price</p>
          </div>
          <div class="fee-item">
            <h4>Bali, Indonesia</h4>
            <p class="fee-amount">Under 5% of purchase price</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fee-includes">
          <h4>What's Included:</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Full property search (40+ properties reviewed weekly)</li>
            <li>All inspections and due diligence</li>
            <li>Expert negotiation on your behalf</li>
            <li>Complete settlement support</li>
            <li>No timeframe pressure, we take as long as needed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-center">
          <a href="/book-free-consultation" class="button-primary">Book a Free Consultation</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-we-work {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 70px;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: var(--body-large);
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .step {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: 35px 30px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-subtle);
    position: relative;
  }

  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: 30px;
    background-color: var(--primary-green);
    color: var(--white);
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .step-icon {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .step h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .step p {
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .step-note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    font-style: italic;
    background-color: #f5f5f5;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--primary-green);
  }

  .fee-transparency {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-subtle);
  }

  .fee-content h3 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .fee-intro {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .fee-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .fee-item {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--primary-green);
  }

  .fee-item h4 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .fee-amount {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .fee-includes {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 20px 25px;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-small);
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .fee-includes h4 {
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .fee-includes ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .fee-includes li {
    padding-left: 28px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .fee-includes li::before {
    content: 'âœ“';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary-green);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .cta-center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .process-steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .fee-details {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .fee-transparency {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
